#: src/threading/parallel-map.md:72
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"// Reject example — Perry rejects this at compile time:\n"
"\n"
"let total = 0;\n"
"\n"
"// COMPILE ERROR: Cannot capture mutable variable 'total'\n"
"parallelMap(data, (item) => {\n"
"    total += item;   // Would be a data race\n"
"    return item;\n"
"});\n"
