msgstr ""

#: src/widgets/creating-widgets.md:93
msgid "Use ternary expressions for conditional rendering:"
msgstr ""

#: src/widgets/creating-widgets.md:95
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"Widget({\n"
"    kind: \"ConditionalWidget\",\n"
